      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist-grade example featuring the S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, an engine renowned for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle body induction. The powertrain is mated to a lightning-quick M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. The chassis architecture remains sharp, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a high-rigidity subframe. This vehicle has been maintained with technical diligence, including a recent oil analysis and throttle actuator service, ensuring the Double-VANOS system and high-pressure internals operate within peak factory tolerances. It is a mechanically robust specimen optimized for lateral G-loading and high-velocity transitions.",
